Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.47,0:00:13.27,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,今天开始就是合宿了么  是要去哪儿来着？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.70,0:00:18.62,Asteroid - Comment,,0,0,0,,注：JAXA即日本宇宙航空研究开发机构
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.70,0:00:18.62,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,地质标本馆和JAXA  是远藤老师提议的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.72,0:00:22.97,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,真好啊  连我的那一份也好好尽兴哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.45,0:00:25.60,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,还有悄悄的把大家的睡脸…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.70,0:00:30.55,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,火箭！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.07,0:00:35.10,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,那个是在科学馆里的实物比例模型哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.02,0:00:38.30,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,老师对这一带很熟悉吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.72,0:00:41.47,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,算是吧  高中的时候住过这儿
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.90,0:00:44.45,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,那是什么  像机器人一样的车
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.37,0:00:47.90,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,吵死了  路都走错了
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,===op===
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.41,0:02:22.70,Asteroid - title,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1100,0)\blur15\pos(600.933,921.466)}04.心跳不止！夏季合宿！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.32,0:02:22.80,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,到啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.27,0:02:24.95,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,难得见你这么兴奋呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.42,0:02:26.82,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,跟平时一样啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.05,0:02:29.27,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,石头标本什么的我也经常在书上看
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.52,0:02:31.92,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,学姐学姐  看这个好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.02,0:02:32.92,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.30,0:02:35.07,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,螳螂蜕下的皮
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.72,0:02:36.80,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.32,0:02:38.90,Asteroid - UP,,0,0,0,,痛痛痛痛痛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.40,0:02:39.80,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,你这家伙真的是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.90,0:02:40.30,Asteroid - UP,,0,0,0,,突然怎么啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.47,0:02:41.62,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.77,0:02:47.17,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,关于暑假合宿  远藤老师说有个很好的提案
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.90,0:02:50.55,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,要不要去我奶奶家？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.97,0:02:53.50,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,哇  这表情…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.22,0:02:56.02,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,没  我是在想这样省下住宿费
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.15,0:02:59.37,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,去参观附近的各种地方怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.82,0:03:00.75,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,各种地方？
