Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.82,0:03:05.03,Asteroid - HandWrite,,0,0,0,,{\fs40\pos(1147.2,626.8)}JAXA\N宇宙中心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.22,0:03:05.37,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,比如说  JAXA宇宙中心  地质标本馆
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.75,0:03:07.42,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,以及地质公园啥的…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.42,0:03:09.15,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,决定了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.40,0:03:14.87,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,好多石头
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.37,0:03:20.87,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,矿物和化石都有
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.15,0:03:22.52,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,好厉害啊小樱…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.22,0:03:26.40,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,这个  就跟图鉴里的石头一模一样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.40,0:03:27.95,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,小猪猪…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.95,0:03:31.82,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,看到樱学姐这么开心  我也很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.17,0:03:34.05,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,我们稍微退远点
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.75,0:03:35.60,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,好…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.87,0:03:40.42,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,找到什么在意的东西么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.87,0:03:41.42,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,这个
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.47,0:03:44.80,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,石头里嵌了金闪闪的骰子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.52,0:03:46.77,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,这边是心型的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.87,0:03:50.85,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,这么漂亮的形状  究竟是怎么形成的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.20,0:03:52.17,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.55,0:03:55.05,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,山梨县石？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.62,0:04:00.32,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,在各地发现的有特点的石头会被认定为「县石」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.72,0:04:02.47,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,我比较中意的是这个
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.15,0:04:04.30,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,樱石？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.75,0:04:06.55,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,是的  这是京都石
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.80,0:04:09.17,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,现在还是天然纪念物呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.45,0:04:12.10,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,真的就像樱花的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.50,0:04:14.37,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,非常可爱而稀少
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.70,0:04:16.57,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,可谓是「高岭之花」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.07,0:04:20.15,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,就如同樱学姐一样的令人憧憬啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.52,0:04:25.10,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,感觉地质班的情绪真是高涨…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.92,0:04:27.95,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,老师在看什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.85,0:04:30.32,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,好多宝石
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.87,0:04:33.77,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,这些全部加起来值多少钱呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.15,0:04:35.02,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,钱…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.37,0:04:37.62,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,梦露学姐  那边的展物是？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.22,0:04:39.62,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,看起来好好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.72,0:04:40.82,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,食欲…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.12,0:04:43.90,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,大…大家尽兴的方式真是各不相同呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.52,0:05:10.47,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,太厉害了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.72,0:05:12.75,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,一天还真是看不完啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.10,0:05:14.70,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,好想一直呆在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.45,0:05:18.15,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,米菈  石头你带来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.45,0:05:19.35,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,带了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.60,0:05:20.35,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,石头？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.57,0:05:23.95,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,其实上次我们在河边烧烤那回
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.97,0:05:27.40,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,米菈捡到的泥岩说不定是化石
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.82,0:05:29.82,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,于是就想要去鉴定一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.07,0:05:32.50,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,摔了一跤把石头给摔开了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.47,0:05:36.10,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,哇这是啥  好吓人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.65,0:05:37.82,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,化石1号…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.32,0:05:40.50,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,米菈  你调查了很多吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.27,0:05:43.22,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,因为不太确定是不是化石
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.42,0:05:45.72,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,就打算先自己研究一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.22,0:05:49.00,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,这本书非常浅显易懂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.25,0:05:50.02,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,真的耶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.42,0:05:52.77,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,哎呀  看上去真有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.07,0:05:54.00,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,绘本…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.90,0:05:58.02,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,我想想  首先动物和植物死后
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.30,0:06:01.32,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,马上就被泥沙给埋住了这点很重要
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.77,0:06:05.15,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,不然的话就会被其他的动物吃掉或者腐烂掉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.42,0:06:08.40,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,然后  被泥的重量给压住
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.70,0:06:10.22,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,或是与矿物进行结合
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.52,0:06:12.02,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,经过数万年后就形成了化石
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.25,0:06:13.67,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,据最近的研究发现
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.80,0:06:16.25,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,好像数周内就能形成哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.62,0:06:19.27,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,也就是说  现在马上就把我埋下的话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.45,0:06:21.47,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,就能作为今年文化祭的展品了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.85,0:06:22.69,Asteroid - HandWrite3,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\pos(860.2,678.467)}米菈的\N化石
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.72,0:06:22.40,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,那可成大事件了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.30,0:06:24.52,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,但是真是惊人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.75,0:06:27.12,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,竟然从河边石头里发现化石
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.55,0:06:29.60,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,也不是那么少见的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.10,0:06:33.47,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,只有有沉积岩的地方  哪儿都有可能
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.70,0:06:36.72,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,这些都是小樱找到的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.75,0:06:40.72,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,这个和这个之外的都是在科学馆买的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.95,0:06:43.10,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,樱学姐太诚实了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.47,0:06:47.65,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,总之  说不定是时隔数万年才重见天日的化石
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.35,0:06:51.40,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,不是很想去弄清楚究竟是什么东西么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.05,0:06:54.17,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,你们这表情是什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.72,0:06:56.20,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,快  抓紧时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.52,0:07:03.35,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,这是在河边捡的石头
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.45,0:07:06.87,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,是在河滩的哪一片区域捡到的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.42,0:07:09.52,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,我想想  应该是在这附近
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.00,0:07:11.62,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,也就是说…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.05,0:07:15.50,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,那个  这是很久以前树叶的化石吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.57,0:07:17.27,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,喂  稍微安静下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.60,0:07:21.47,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,这个黑色的痕纹  说不定不是化石呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.50,0:07:26.22,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,但是刚刚樱学姐都一口咬定那么说了…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.27,0:07:28.17,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,安静点啊我说
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.90,0:07:31.15,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,你们听说过「忍石」吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.67,0:07:33.87,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,忍石？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.52,0:07:37.07,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,是的  也叫作「树枝石」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.45,0:07:39.72,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,在石头缝隙中混入了锰
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.00,0:07:42.30,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,就会变成植物一样的形状
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.92,0:07:47.45,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,因为很容易和化石搞混  所以也被叫做「假化石」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.05,0:07:49.82,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,假的化石…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.47,0:07:51.47,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,不  但是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.77,0:07:52.32,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,看这儿
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.91,0:07:55.32,Asteroid - HandWrite3,,0,0,0,,{\3c&HE0F2CB&\4c&HE0F2CB&\b1\frz350\pos(780,711)}鳞片
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.82,0:07:55.10,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,大概三厘米大小  有些发光的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.47,0:07:57.70,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,这应该是鱼的鳞片吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.70,0:08:01.75,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,还有些更小的很难看清的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.25,0:08:04.80,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,在这标签的前面有几条小的纹路吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.07,0:08:05.80,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,能看清吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.62,0:08:07.55,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,用这个来看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.22,0:08:10.10,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,有了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.22,0:08:13.25,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,这个大概是海绵动物的骨针
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.55,0:08:18.05,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,是在前寒武纪末期生活在海里的生物的骨组织
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.52,0:08:21.60,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,虽然很小  但这也是了不起的化石哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.97,0:08:22.80,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,化石…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.25,0:08:25.07,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,化石！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.25,0:08:27.95,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,化石
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.12,0:08:29.80,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,化石化石…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.12,0:08:33.75,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,给你们这个
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.15,0:08:36.65,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,这是发现那个石头周边的地质图解说
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.95,0:08:38.22,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,非常感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.47,0:08:41.20,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,地层的名字以及历史
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.60,0:08:43.50,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,连容易找到的化石也标了出来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.97,0:08:46.47,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,这份资料在网上也能查阅
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.80,0:08:47.92,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,要学一下怎么查吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.37,0:08:49.10,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,是的！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.20,0:08:56.70,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,地质班睡着了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.25,0:08:58.90,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,因为情报量太大了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.37,0:09:01.92,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,特别是小樱  闹尽兴了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.12,0:09:02.75,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.02,0:09:05.40,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,像小孩一样  比平时还可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.70,0:09:08.90,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,樱学姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.30,0:09:10.15,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,完全叫不醒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.40,0:09:15.27,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,你也不是小孩了稍微走两步啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.60,0:09:18.07,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,幸  还有学生们
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.22,0:09:20.52,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,欢迎  路程辛苦了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.92,0:09:22.00,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.20,0:09:23.47,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.00,0:09:25.77,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,米菈  你看老爷爷的帽子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.12,0:09:27.72,Asteroid - UP,,0,0,0,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.76,0:09:29.70,Asteroid - UP,,0,0,0,,欢迎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.82,0:09:27.67,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,JAXA？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.85,0:09:29.70,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,难道说老爷爷是那儿的职员？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.20,0:09:33.02,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,但是感觉字体有点不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.00,0:09:35.72,Asteroid - UP,,0,0,0,,JA
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.00,0:09:35.67,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,农协？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.42,0:09:38.92,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,是喜欢宇宙的农家老爷爷
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.40,0:09:41.02,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,稍微宽容一些吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.77,0:09:48.90,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.37,0:09:51.57,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,我们是星咲高中地学部
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.06,0:09:49.02,Asteroid - HandWrite2,,0,0,0,,{\frz14.97\pos(420,516)}收集情报
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.06,0:09:49.02,Asteroid - HandWrite2,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1408,330)}我们在寻找小行星
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.57,0:09:52.35,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,那是啥…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.90,0:09:56.35,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,好像是合宿前两人想出来的作战
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.80,0:10:00.17,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,在宇宙中心那么做  看上去只像是在胡闹…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.10,0:10:02.80,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,但是被搭话了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.80,0:10:06.12,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,拿到糖了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.60,0:10:09.60,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.85,0:10:11.75,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,参观学习的集合点在…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.05,0:10:14.85,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,爷爷…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.50,0:10:18.22,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,爷爷似乎很想来的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.42,0:10:20.45,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,一起来不是也挺好的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.22,0:10:25.40,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,没事没事  这是属于你们的合宿
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.20,0:10:27.27,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,火箭！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.62,0:10:29.60,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,昨天看到的虽然是模型
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.87,0:10:32.85,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,这是连内部都有做的真正的火箭哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.05,0:10:33.92,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,真正的？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.85,0:10:36.00,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,我想摸摸看
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.40,0:10:37.70,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,我说梦露
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.92,0:10:39.25,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,天文班也太吵了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.67,0:10:42.27,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,你也有点部长的样子稍微管管…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.05,0:10:45.85,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,摸不到
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.95,0:10:47.35,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,宇宙好遥远啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.90,0:10:52.62,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,大家关系很好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.87,0:10:54.67,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.05,0:10:57.50,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,好厉害啊  蓝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.50,0:10:58.72,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,是宇宙中心哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.05,0:11:01.77,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,能不能找到关于发现小行星的线索呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.97,0:11:02.35,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.82,0:11:05.30,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,你们俩  对小行星感兴趣么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.57,0:11:09.22,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,讨厌啦老师  入部那一天不是就说过的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.27,0:11:11.80,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,是这样吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.80,0:11:14.10,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,学姐  来拍纪念照吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.47,0:11:16.55,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,这样啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.12,0:11:21.02,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,欢迎大家参加参观学习
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.65,0:11:23.97,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,首先请观看介绍影片
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.22,0:11:31.60,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,这儿是日本离宇宙最近的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.80,0:11:34.42,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,欢迎来到宇宙中心
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.85,0:11:39.85,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,在这里将为你介绍JAXA的各种项目
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.00,0:11:45.32,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,宇宙太厉害了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.87,0:11:47.40,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,人类太厉害了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.80,0:11:48.52,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,小米菈？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.77,0:11:50.87,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,这又不是那种催人泪下的影片
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.35,0:11:54.10,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,上了年纪真是不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.00,0:11:56.72,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,我们原来是少数派么…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.55,0:12:00.95,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,接下来将参观宇航员养成楼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.52,0:12:04.27,Asteroid - UP,,0,0,0,,通常的话只能是员工进入的区域
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.10,0:12:05.57,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,梦露学姐  表情变得比平时认真呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.32,0:12:06.50,Asteroid - UP,,0,0,0,,所以请大家紧紧跟随我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.90,0:12:08.45,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,应该有很多想法吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.37,0:12:10.75,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,毕竟这是她向往的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.40,0:12:12.22,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,向往？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.82,0:12:17.00,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,这边的宇航服约重120千克
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.27,0:12:20.47,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,配备有生命维持装置  氧气以及电池
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.90,0:12:22.75,Asteroid - UP,,0,0,0,,当然  在舱外活动时…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.47,0:12:26.57,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,窗户里边是封闭坏境的训练设备
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.07,0:12:33.55,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,上回的选拔考试从963名报名者中挑选了10名在这里边参加了考试
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.07,0:12:37.45,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,那个  成为宇航员的条件是什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.70,0:12:39.77,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,我想想…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.25,0:12:41.95,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,首先需要身体健康
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.30,0:12:43.65,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,擅长英语
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.02,0:12:46.62,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,最重要的是具有协同性
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.10,0:12:49.15,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,这一点是最重要的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.62,0:12:50.75,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,谢谢您
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.07,0:12:51.62,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,不客气
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.20,0:12:53.92,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,听到了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.07,0:12:55.12,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,小樱…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.82,0:12:57.50,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.10,0:13:00.75,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,发音要稍微再加油一下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.57,0:13:04.92,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,我们也去向大姐姐问一下小行星的事情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.77,0:13:08.60,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,小行星吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.15,0:13:12.17,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,没错  说不定会成为找到小行星的提示
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.62,0:13:16.22,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,我只是个导览  详细的并不是太清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.57,0:13:20.20,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,我想展示馆里的解说员可能会知道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.57,0:13:21.87,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.02,0:13:22.82,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,真是抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.05,0:13:24.85,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,没有的  真是多谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.15,0:13:28.85,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,好！敌在展示馆
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.20,0:13:30.20,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,出发吧  蓝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.57,0:13:31.10,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.60,0:13:37.60,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,是人工卫星啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.97,0:13:53.35,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,有隼鸟号的展览
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.97,0:13:53.35,Asteroid - Comment,,0,0,0,,注：隼鸟号是日本的小行星探测器
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.90,0:13:54.82,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,这里的话一定能…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.90,0:13:57.95,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,那个  打扰一下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.82,0:14:02.27,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,你们想要寻找小行星吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.92,0:14:05.35,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,请问你有没有什么提示…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.95,0:14:06.87,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,提示啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.42,0:14:10.75,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,或者您知道对于这方面比较了解的人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.25,0:14:17.02,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,这中心基本是宇宙开发活动的展示
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.60,0:14:19.75,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,虽然也有小行星探索机器的展示
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.05,0:14:22.05,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,对于新天体的探索发现
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.05,0:14:26.62,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,全国的其他据点的话应该会有这方面的专家
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.32,0:14:29.87,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,这样啊  十分感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.17,0:14:31.10,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,十分感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.32,0:14:31.92,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,不客气
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.65,0:14:33.97,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,十分感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.72,0:14:36.50,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,没有找到线索
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.85,0:14:38.85,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,蓝  我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.27,0:14:42.42,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,但是也学到了很多  弄懂了很多事情
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.92,0:14:46.57,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,比如一个个地去全国的其他据点
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.77,0:14:48.80,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,总有一天能遇见这方面的专家
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.77,0:14:52.25,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,乐观过头了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.55,0:14:54.65,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,小樱  帮得漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.97,0:14:57.00,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,真是看不下去了…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.10,0:15:00.77,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,你也去帮下她们啊  你的协同性呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.90,0:15:04.45,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,老师  参观结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.40,0:15:06.47,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.72,0:15:09.70,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,是宇宙食品  有卖各种各样的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.37,0:15:12.30,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,宇宙服仿制品
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.97,0:15:14.87,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,老师买了什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.90,0:15:17.20,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,我才是想问你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.60,0:15:20.77,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,那么  差不多该回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.50,0:15:23.07,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,咦  梦露呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.62,0:15:25.07,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,去洗手间了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.37,0:15:38.90,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,去了挺久呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.42,0:15:40.37,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,你这表情怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.90,0:15:42.42,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,宇宙真是遥远
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.02,0:15:46.92,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,欢迎回来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.17,0:15:48.95,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,烧烤已经准备好了哟
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.90,0:15:51.15,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,就像是祭典一样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.70,0:15:55.10,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,爷爷在闲暇的时间里可是很努力的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.60,0:15:58.80,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,没有带上你真是抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.27,0:16:00.70,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,作为道歉  这个给你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.12,0:16:02.82,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,幸…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.00,0:16:09.62,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,今天是满月啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.10,0:16:13.50,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,对的  所以今天很难看见星星
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.35,0:16:17.77,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,这个时候  赏月也不错呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.10,0:16:20.47,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,既然难得  把望远镜拿出来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.00,0:16:23.75,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,同学们  能稍微帮下忙吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.07,0:16:24.90,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.30,0:16:28.57,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,哇 架台是赤道仪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.95,0:16:31.37,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,和地学部的部件不太一样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.97,0:16:36.40,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,地学部的架台是转动横竖的经纬台
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.80,0:16:40.82,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,爷爷的是随着地球的自转转动的赤道仪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.57,0:16:46.17,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,赤道仪的话只需要转动一个旋钮就能一直锁定  太方便了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.07,0:16:49.85,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,我也想看
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.10,0:16:54.35,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,原本以为月亮会更坑坑洼洼的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.07,0:16:57.00,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,没想到这么滑溜溜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.80,0:17:02.72,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,那是因为满月的时候  太阳光从正面照射到月亮
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.05,0:17:05.25,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,环形山的突起就很难看清
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.67,0:17:09.97,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,顺带一提  环形山比较多的亮部  主要由斜长岩组成
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.57,0:17:12.75,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,暗部主要由玄武岩组成
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.82,0:17:14.97,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.97,0:17:18.10,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,松了口气
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.40,0:17:20.22,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,学了很多吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.35,0:17:24.32,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,你们也稍微学一下石头的知识啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.97,0:17:26.52,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,拿我们撒气
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.82,0:17:28.90,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,喂  吃西瓜了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.17,0:17:29.92,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,西瓜！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.40,0:17:32.42,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,对了这个
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.75,0:17:35.22,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,这是幸拜托我找的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.85,0:17:37.87,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,找到了啊  谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.70,0:17:40.55,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,旧的宣传单？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.80,0:17:44.27,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,面向高中生  寻找新天体项目？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.77,0:17:46.57,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,这是什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.79,0:17:46.75,Asteroid - HandWrite4,,0,0,0,,{\pos(820,290)}KIRA星
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.79,0:17:46.75,Asteroid - HandWrite4,,0,0,0,,{\c&H845929&\pos(1466,894)}挑战
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.79,0:17:46.75,Asteroid - HandWrite4 - up,,0,0,0,,{\pos(820,290)}KIRA星
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.79,0:17:46.75,Asteroid - HandWrite4 - up,,0,0,0,,{\c&H845929&\pos(1466,894)}挑战
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.95,0:17:51.35,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,是暑假时在天文台举办的一个叫「KIRA星挑战」的项目
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.82,0:17:54.97,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,我以前也参加过哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.37,0:17:57.32,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,可是那时候没有找到
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.40,0:18:02.30,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,为什么要把这么厉害的情报藏着
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.55,0:18:05.32,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,我都不知道你们的梦想…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.70,0:18:08.05,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,但是入部的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.65,0:18:10.82,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,抱歉  我在隔壁房间睡着了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.72,0:18:12.45,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,睡着了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.32,0:18:17.35,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,今年的报名截止日期已经过了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.98,0:18:18.11,Asteroid - Chat,,0,0,0,,{\frz15.21\pos(918.8,396.8)}本活动报名已结束
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.40,0:18:21.35,Asteroid - UP,,0,0,0,,要是能够早点发现就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.82,0:18:21.82,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,地点在石垣島
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.37,0:18:23.50,Asteroid - UP,,0,0,0,,果然生气了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.07,0:18:23.97,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,在冲绳啊  真好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.62,0:18:26.77,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,石垣島…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.52,0:18:28.17,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,冲绳…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.02,0:18:30.02,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,蓝色大海…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.45,0:18:31.05,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,米菈？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.25,0:18:33.45,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,KIRA星挑战
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.27,0:18:36.25,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,参加对象为全国高中生
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.90,0:18:39.27,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,根据提出的课题选出七名参加
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.57,0:18:43.57,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,竞争激烈  而且也不一定能发现啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.12,0:18:48.55,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,但是我感觉稍微前进了一两步
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.87,0:18:49.35,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.00,0:18:52.30,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,也许是大跳了一步呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.70,0:18:53.07,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.77,0:18:58.42,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,真是怀念
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.90,0:19:00.97,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,那时候从石垣島回来的你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.07,0:19:03.70,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,眼神也和那群孩子一样闪耀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.15,0:19:12.97,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,参观JAXA  BBQ  还有天体观测
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.45,0:19:14.70,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,最后放烟花
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.12,0:19:16.62,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,你玩太拼了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.00,0:19:21.50,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,话说回来  没想到老师曾经参加过寻找小行星呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.72,0:19:23.47,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,完全不知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.67,0:19:25.77,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,我一直都很兴奋
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.62,0:19:30.97,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,也就是说  天文班三人都更加接近目标了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.37,0:19:32.27,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,三个都？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.27,0:19:34.00,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.25,0:19:37.02,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,想成为宇航员
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.32,0:19:38.50,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,宇航员?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.90,0:19:39.52,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.22,0:19:40.62,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.10,0:19:43.72,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,所以今天才那么认真啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.07,0:19:47.10,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,是个过于远大的梦想  有些羞耻
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.37,0:19:50.30,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,对自己的梦想说羞耻是不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.12,0:19:52.60,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,如果是认真追求的话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.10,0:19:57.10,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,对于还没有确定具体目标的我来说
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.77,0:19:59.87,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,你们这样真的很厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.82,0:20:03.65,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,对自己的梦想不要顾虑
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.45,0:20:07.40,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,小樱  谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.07,0:20:10.65,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,也就是说
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.92,0:20:13.05,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,并不是在生我们的气
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.42,0:20:15.80,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,我不是在激励你们吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.05,0:20:17.90,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,太难懂了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.50,0:20:20.70,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,对自己的梦想不要顾虑
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.65,0:20:26.47,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,我好像找到了自己想做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.02,0:20:30.25,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,其实  我有一个想去的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.20,0:20:32.66,Asteroid - Chat,,0,0,0,,{\c&HB39DA0&\pos(345.6,543.6)}地图和测量科学馆
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.12,0:20:34.27,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,这里是绘制地图的据点
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.77,0:20:36.00,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,国土地理院
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.47,0:20:41.80,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,没想到猪濑对这方面有兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.45,0:20:45.42,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,虽然原计划改变了  你们没意见吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.62,0:20:47.07,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,完全不介意
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.57,0:20:48.15,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,而且
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.07,0:20:52.87,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,看到那样的神情  我想谁都不会抱怨的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.98,0:20:57.69,Asteroid - Chat2,,0,0,0,,{\pos(832,167)}筑波VLBI天线
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.82,0:21:01.47,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,难怪感觉有一些伤感
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.30,0:21:04.25,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,老师  怎么了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.40,0:21:10.42,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,在那里原本有一座特别大的碟形天线
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.47,0:21:25.57,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,老师！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.17,0:21:28.27,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,这里有天线哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.82,0:21:30.77,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,不再沉溺于过去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.95,0:21:32.15,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,感觉打起精神了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.25,0:21:39.57,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,通过这次的合宿  了解了学姐们新的一面
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.05,0:21:42.82,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,通过参观学到了各种事情
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.30,0:21:45.60,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,感觉大家的世界都变宽阔了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.45,0:21:51.75,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,虽然寻找小行星这一梦想还很模糊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.72,0:21:56.27,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,但像是在河畔找到的  很小的化石一样的星星
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.77,0:21:57.82,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,一定存在着
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.97,0:22:00.62,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,存在于这片天空的某处
