Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.45,0:00:59.33,Asteroid - OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(450,0)}未来一定就在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.66,0:01:05.00,Asteroid - OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(450,0)}所以迈开步伐启程吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.68,0:01:24.68,Asteroid - OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(450,0)}喜欢的事物无论何时
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.68,0:01:28.65,Asteroid - OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(450,0)}都想要无所忧虑的继续下去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.69,0:01:34.24,Asteroid - OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(450,0)}难为情的部分和迷茫一起扔掉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.24,0:01:37.74,Asteroid - OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(450,0)}剩下的只有勇气
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.62,0:01:44.45,Asteroid - OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(450,0)}无论从哪个角度去看
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.45,0:01:49.83,Asteroid - OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(450,0)}世界都很广阔啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.21,0:01:56.26,Asteroid - OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(450,450)}没有见过的事物  想要去找到
